last_text: Vaia, thanks for the recognition; I am very happy. vaia, Thank you for putting up with my bad attitude and approaches for such a long time. I recognize many of my negative attitudes, and sometimes your anger helps me identify them. I was initially sad, but I later realized that those were blessings and guidelines for my self-improvement, and I am working to change those negative attitudes through practice so that they become habits. take care vaia.
